subject: Basketball (College)
NCAA Basketball Championships (Men)
lead_paragraph: Kaminsky and his teammates were treated to the quintessential Los Angeles experience during a trip that ended with the Badgers’ successful defense of their West Regional title in the N.C.A.A. tournament.
